<component id="ID_txt02">
<text><![CDATA[<ul><li>The native TCP/IP naming system relies on a file called a HOSTS file and contains the name and IP address of known hosts.</li><br/><li>DNS is a hostname resolution system that solves the shortcomings of the HOSTS file for name resolution.</li><br/><li>The structure of DNS is hierarchical and DNS database files are distributed among root, top level domains, second level domains, and subdomains.</li></ul>]]></text>
</component>

